OL,4,G1650FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GSurrey. Drum tutor Rob hopes that
OL,6,     Ghis Thai-tastic menu will wow his
OL,7,     Gguests - especially the object of
OL,8,     Ghis affections, Petrina.
OL,9,G1720FCome Dine with Me
OL,10,     GSurrey. Singing teacher Petrina
OL,11,     Ghopes that her experience
OL,12,     Gentertaining on cruise ships will
OL,13,     Ggive her evening the edge. And
OL,14,     Gher salted caramel chocolate
OL,15,     Gdessert serves up a surprise.
OL,16,G1750FCome Dine with Me
OL,17,     GSurrey. On the final night,
OL,18,     GGiovanni flies the flag for
OL,19,     GSicily with some family recipes.
OL,20,     GBut he has a tagliatelle tragedy.
