OL,4,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GNa'im and Sara host first at
OL,6,     Gtheir hotel in the breathtaking
OL,7,     GCumbrian countryside. But one
OL,8,     Gpair are too preoccupied with the
OL,9,     Gfurniture to care about the view.
OL,10,G1855FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GNeil and Jack host at their hotel
OL,12,     Gnear majestic Windermere, where
OL,13,     Gthe B&Bers enjoy yet more
OL,14,     Gstunning views. But there's still
OL,15,     Gnegativity in the feedback.
OL,16,G1925FFour in a Bed
OL,17,     GAt Chris's glampsite in Richmond,
OL,18,     GNorth Yorkshire, off-grid really
OL,19,     Gdoes mean off the electricity
OL,20,     Ggrid. Which is quite a worry for
OL,21,     Gsome of the B&Bers...
